definitions.definition: A town and civil parish with a town council in north-west Herefordshire , England ( OS grid ref SO2956 ) .
A village and civil parish (served by Kington and Dormston Parish Council) in Wychavon district, Worcestershire , England ( OS grid ref SO9856 ) .
A habitational surname from Old English .
